"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-sport-509577-olympic-equestrian-suspended-for-wearing-mankini-during-competition\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australian Olympic equestrian rider Shane Rose has been stood down from competition for wearing a mankini during a show jumping event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9981037521731319, \"rank\": 0.0016053184857548848, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic equestrian rider Shane Rose has been stood down from competition for several days for wearing a mankini during a showjumping event, after concerns were raised about his attire to Equestrian Australia.\", \"from\": 136, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.999882979177413, \"rank\": 0.00011703256589879656, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}, {\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisation, which runs Australia's elite equestrian programme has confirmed it stood Rose down after he wore the revealing costume during a fancy dress event last weekend at Wallaby Hill in the Southern Highlands.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9870555613058865, \"rank\": 0.01214127253646221, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_1920_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"equestrian programme\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_1920_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_1920_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9429638425501287, \"rank\": 0.05616539199837511, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Equestrian Australia raised concerns about Shane Rose's attire during the event.Photo:Shane Rose Instagram  Rose said he was amazed by the reaction, after hearing that the story was being reported by the BBC and the South China News.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9429638425501287, \"rank\": 0.05616539199837511, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}, {\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.980212857689882, \"rank\": 0.020010985856856893, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}, {\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_News_Service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_News_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_News_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought I was just having a bit of fun in a dress up competition ... certainly things have gone a bit crazy,\\\" Rose said.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9429638425501287, \"rank\": 0.05616539199837511, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rose said it was an unofficial event and he thought the decision to dress up would not be taken too seriously.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9429638425501287, \"rank\": 0.05616539199837511, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not set out to offend anyone and I am sorry if I overstepped the mark, but I was just having a bit of a laugh and I think if you can not have a bit of fun in sport then there is no point in doing it.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never worn one [a mankini] before and it was not a very comfortable experience so I can not imagine I will be wearing one anytime soon.\\\"\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement on its website, Equestrian Australia said it had an obligation to address the concerns, but insists the 50 year old has not been suspended.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Concerns were raised to Equestrian Australia and the government sporting agencies regarding Shane Rose's attire at a recent closed event at Wallaby Hill, images of which were subsequently shared on social media,\\\" it said.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As with any high performance athlete, Shane is bound by the High Performance and Equestrian Australia Codes of Conduct and Athlete Agreement.\\\"\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A decision on any further disciplinary action is expected as early as this week.\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This does not affect his ability to train or otherwise participate in the sport,\\\" Equestrian Australia said.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Equestrian Australia is dedicated to supporting our athletes in their Olympic campaign and works collaboratively with them to achieve their Olympic dreams.\\\"\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A silver and bronze medallist at three Olympic Games, Rose is preparing for the Paris Olympics and is hoping it is a storm in a teacup.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2324, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9429638425501287, \"rank\": 0.05616539199837511, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They [Equestrian Australian] have to go through a process, I am hoping in the next day or two there'll be a resolution and I am hoping it will go in my favour and we can look back on this as a bit of fun so fingers crossed,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9981037521731319, \"rank\": 0.0016053184857548848, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo:Facebook - Shane Rose  Rose removed a Facebook post and issued an apology on his personal social media.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9429638425501287, \"rank\": 0.05616539199837511, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you for the support.\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not my intention to have this issue escalated any more so my previous post has been removed,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the comments in response to his post were in support of his dress-up during the event, describing Rose as \\\"a larrikin\\\".\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like this apology is completely unnecessary and come on Equestrian Australia, this is ridiculous!!!\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3085, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", one said.\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The majority are behind you Shane Rose Eventing,\\\" said another.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This story was first published bythe ABC  Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  for ad-free news and current affairs  We haveregular online commentaryof local and international sport.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3245, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999082001565, \"rank\": 9.179985576177914e-08, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.9996848112038222, \"rank\": 0.00031528817157083934, \"text\": \"Radio New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3396, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 0.9998794955741411, \"rank\": 0.00012051879300532243, \"text\": \"RSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}, {\"begin\": 3408, \"end\": 3411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}